						               													<description>In Mythic, you are an Overseer &amp;mdash; a mortal being striving to join the Order of the Mythic and obtain immortality. Gain fame by defeating other Overseers in combat with the powers gifted to you by the Order, and take on step closer to being recognized as worthy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played on two 3x3 grids with each player having a 40-card main deck and a 20-card Soul Deck. Players alternate going through all of the phases of their turn, managing their resource, their offence, and their defense in an attempt to defeat their opponent. Players are trying to deal 60 Soul Damage, destroy the opponent&amp;rsquo;s Soul Spire, or run their opponent out of cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mythic is a unique game that blends many popular aspects of gaming into one cohesive and balanced game. It has a Mythology theme that stays true to traditional lore, dynamic RPG battle elements like ranged combat, movement and resistances, traditional trading card game depth of strategy and familiarity, mixed with its own unique resource management system.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
